body:
Cheesepuffs

Out of curiosity have we all forgotten that Jandi had a cheesepuffs scene too? It was just… it was kind of a mess is all 😂 Is it still proof of their endgame status? Maybe. It might also be representative of the mess their relationship has been as they try to get to endgame status, but who am I to judge, I’m just a jerk with a tumblr

but honestly all of their cheesepuffs scenes are kinda representative of their relationship dynamics. Jandi, failing at being honest, vulnerable, and communicative. Muffy, where Buffy doesn’t want a relationship and is “just here for the” friendship. Tyrus, communicative, straightforward, and caring.
